Package entity

Class Applicant

java.lang.Object
entity.User
entity.Applicant
Direct Known Subclasses:
Officer
public class Applicant extends User
Models an applicant in the BTO management system. They can view available BTO project listings, apply for available projects, make enquiries, and view their application statuses.
